description: The complete package of flavor and fun times is rolling down the street with Kona Ice! Kona Ice Lil Music City is bringing the best tropical shaved ice right to you with all their great flavors ready and waiting for your personal touch. Groovy Grape, Blue Raspberry, Strawberry fresh, and more! Add and mix to your hearts content while enjoying the tropical atmosphere that Kona Ice brings!
name: Kona Ice Lil Music City
